&lt;li&gt;Excellent analytical and problem-solving skills.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Effective communication and teamwork abilities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proficiency in Microsoft Office.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prior work experience is desired.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
